{"tid":555814,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"前曼聯中場與世長辭　享年36歲","createTime":"2018-02-10T00:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T05:48:35.000Z","uid":20933,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"94b17c79386721199dada63a362ee9ccdfb9e403","tid":555814,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T00:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180210/large/1518220420_2495.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180210%2Flarge%2F1518220420_2495.jpg&h=31e8fdac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國《BBC》報道，確診患上胰腺癌的前曼聯中場里安米拿（Liam Miller）周五晚與世長辭，終年36歲。<br />\n<br />\n里安米拿生前曾經效力包括些路迪、曼聯、列斯聯、新特蘭、昆士柏流浪等英國知名球會，其辭世的消息是由一家他生前曾經效力兩個球季的蘇超球隊喜伯年公佈。終年36歲的里安米拿於2000年在些路迪展開其職業足球生涯，四年後轉投曼聯。同年他躋身愛爾蘭大國腳的行列，至2009年共21次在國際賽上陣。<br />\n<br />\n里安米拿是在去年11月確診患上胰腺癌，他在美國接受治療後，再返回出生地、愛爾蘭的確克（Cork）接受化療，惜最終亦不敵癌症，在37歲生日前四天辭世。"},{"pid":"4d39c1365e2ea3ac517081a0a09eb725fcb33779","tid":555814,"uid":67225,"like":5,"dislike":34,"score":-29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T05:09:39.000Z","msg":"居然無反獌進場"},{"pid":"04a713add6b01c2002a3903647b9075b05627bd1","tid":555814,"uid":153600,"like":31,"dislike":4,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T05:11:47.000Z","msg":"rip<br />\n抽水死全家"},{"pid":"918a4f0aefa7bbe4b9daee4566d95bd149f0c267","tid":555814,"uid":143582,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T05:13:20.000Z","msg":"唔識，不過都rip <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d078642d6cd2752aa367fe690cf63d48e882b9cb","tid":555814,"uid":7638,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"quote":{"pid":"4d39c1365e2ea3ac517081a0a09eb725fcb33779","tid":555814,"uid":67225,"like":5,"dislike":34,"score":-29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T05:09:39.000Z","msg":"居然無反獌進場"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T05:27:08.000Z","msg":"佢又唔係d咩犯眾憎既人，踢曼聯又唔係多，普通球員一個，仲要咁後生就過左生。係咪咁都要人入黎揾交嗌，小學雞咩"},{"pid":"cf163f81c55b8c3f2dd39a6f1b553da94e6